1
00:00:01,352 --> 00:00:04,570
<i>- Previously on</i> The Resident...
- I loved my sister very much.

2
00:00:04,605 --> 00:00:07,623
One night, I decided to take a
quick nap, and when I woke up,

3
00:00:07,658 --> 00:00:09,408
the whole house was on fire.

4
00:00:09,443 --> 00:00:11,794
- How's Jessie?
- Her kidneys are failing.

5
00:00:11,829 --> 00:00:13,306
I was a project for you,
and now it's finished.

6
00:00:13,330 --> 00:00:14,591
Tell me I'm wrong.
Tell me I'm right.

7
00:00:14,615 --> 00:00:16,248
Either way, just open up

8
00:00:16,283 --> 00:00:18,717
- like you asked me to do.
- And I will.

9
00:00:18,752 --> 00:00:20,969
When I'm ready, when
I figure some things out.

10
00:00:21,004 --> 00:00:22,649
I mean, my feelings
aren't just gonna change.

11
00:00:22,673 --> 00:00:24,417
Conrad and I have fought long
and hard for our relationship.

12
00:00:24,441 --> 00:00:25,691
We've been through it.

13
00:00:25,726 --> 00:00:26,942
But I love him.

14
00:00:29,279 --> 00:00:30,712
♪ <i>Get up offa that thing...</i> ♪

15
00:00:30,747 --> 00:00:32,497
Come on!

16
