♪ <i>Get up offa that thing</i> ♪

17
00:00:34,402 --> 00:00:36,769
♪ <i>And dance till
you, sing it now</i> ♪

18
00:00:36,804 --> 00:00:39,332
♪ <i>Get up offa that thing</i> ♪

19
